:GRAPH GRAPH
:SCALE
:VAR total number of HB
:UNITS HB/Month
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR HB by members of the OC
:UNITS HB/Month
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR HB by occasional thieves
:UNITS HB/Month
:LINE-WIDTH 2

:GRAPH GRAPH_0
:SCALE
:VAR effective chance of being caught for HB in NL
:Y-MIN 0.15
:Y-MAX 0.25
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:SCALE
:VAR members of OC active in HB in NL
:UNITS members
:Y-MIN 2400
:Y-MAX 2700
:LINE-WIDTH 2

:GRAPH GRAPH_1
:SCALE
:VAR HB by members of the OC
:UNITS HB/Month
:Y-MIN 9000
:Y-MAX 12000
:DATASET Q4
:VAR HB by members of the OC
:DATASET Q5sens1
:VAR HB by members of the OC
:DATASET Q5sens2

:GRAPH GRAPH_2
:SCALE
:VAR HB by occasional thieves
:UNITS HB/Month
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 25000
:DATASET Q4
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR HB by occasional thieves
:DATASET Q5sens1
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR HB by occasional thieves
:DATASET Q5sens2
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR total number of HB
:DATASET Q4
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR total number of HB
:DATASET Q5sens1
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR total number of HB
:DATASET Q5sens2
:LINE-WIDTH 2
